# 📚 Chat with Multiple PDFs

An AI-powered chatbot that lets you upload multiple PDF files and ask questions about them in natural language.

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 [Click here to use the app](https://hafsa3368-multiple-pdf-chatbot.streamlit.app/)

## 💡 Features
- Upload multiple PDF files at once
- Ask questions in natural language
- AI answers only from your uploaded documents
- Chat history maintained during session
- Fast responses using Groq LLM

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **Streamlit** — Web UI
- **PyPDF2** — PDF text extraction
- **HuggingFace Embeddings** — Text to vectors
- **FAISS** — Vector similarity search
- **Groq + Llama 3.3 70B** — AI language model
- **LangChain** — AI pipeline

## ⚙️ How to Run Locally

**1. Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/hafsa3368/Multiple-pdf-chatbot.git
cd Multiple-pdf-chatbot
```

**2. Create virtual environment**
```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
```

**3. Install dependencies**
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

**4. Create .env file**
```
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
```

**5. Run the app**
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

## 📌 How to Use
1. Upload one or more PDF files from the sidebar
2. Click **"Process"** button
3. Type your question in the chat box
4. Get instant AI-powered answers!

